<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="half-n">half <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /hɑːf/    美 /hæf/  </p>
<p>[C] (pl halves)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>半；一半：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an hour and a half / one and a half hours 
一个半小时</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The half of six is three. 
6的一半是3。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Cut the <strong>apple in half / into halves</strong>. 
把苹果切成两半。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(比赛、音乐会等) 半场；半局：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>France played very well <strong>in the first half</strong>. 
上半场，法国队发挥得不错。</p></div></div>